Benchmarks for 2D canvas drawImage variations
  + pixel-aligned
  + transformed
  + with different image sources
    http://jsperf.com/canvas-drawimage
  + different composite ops
  + different ways to do spritesheets (cache to individual canvases 
    vs cropping on the fly)
    http://jsperf.com/canvas-spritesheets

Benchmarks for WebGL texture upload
  - different image sources (img, video, canvas, arraybuffer)
  - different pixelstorei params

Benchmarks for 2D canvas path creation
  + create complex small path, fill
    http://jsperf.com/canvas-path

Benchmarks for 2D canvas text draw
  + filled text & stroked text
    http://jsperf.com/canvas-filltext-stroketext
  + different font sizes
    http://jsperf.com/canvas-fontsizes

Benchmarks for different ways to do blitting
  + fillRect with 1px rects
  + putImageData
  http://jsperf.com/canvas-blitting
  http://jsperf.com/canvas-blitting-full
  - work in typed array, upload as texture to webgl
